Package com.dukes.lang.parser Description

Describes an abstract interpretation of any programming language parser. However, given the types parsers available, this currently only holds an abstract implementation of a table parser. This does not disallow any parser, as the Parser class is what will be passed on to the semantic analyzer.

Exceptions provided include ParsingException and InvalidStackValueException. Each is explain in detail within their class.

Since:
0.2.0
